OL,3,CThe 'distressing' and 'demeaning'
OL,4,Ctreatment of women in police custody
OL,6,FA damning report has found women and
OL,7,Fgirls were left naked after
OL,8,F"demeaning" strip searches, covered in
OL,9,Ftheir own blood, and unable to use the
OL,10,Ftoilet while in police custody.
OL,12,FDame Vera Baird's inquiry has shone a
OL,13,Flight on some of the worst experiences
OL,14,Fof females - many extremely vulnerable
OL,15,F- arrested and held in Greater
OL,16,FManchester Police custody.
