OL,3,CThe 'distressing' and 'demeaning'
OL,4,Ctreatment of women in police custody
OL,6,FMore than 15 people - including two
OL,7,Fmen - gave evidence to the report,
OL,8,Fhighlighting the force's "shocking
OL,9,Fdisregard for rights of those coming
OL,10,Finto contact with the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem".
OL,13,FOf those 15, Dame Vera found seven had
OL,14,Fbeen unlawfully arrested.
OL,16,FCustody records, detention logs, crime
OL,17,Freports, witness statements and CCTV
OL,18,Ffootage were among documents and data
OL,19,Fthat were trawled through.
