OL,9,Fquestions about the culture at GMP.
OL,11,F"My findings show that there is
OL,12,Fsignificant and, indeed, urgent work
OL,13,Frequired if the public of Greater
OL,14,FManchester are to have full confidence
OL,15,Fin their police force."
