OL,6,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham,
OL,7,Fwho oversees GMP said the report
OL,8,F"reveals is a problematic culture and
OL,9,Fpractices that must change".
OL,11,FHe added: "As people will be able to
OL,12,Fread in the personal narratives, many
OL,13,Fof those people were vulnerable before
OL,14,Ftheir arrest, as survivors of domestic
OL,15,For sexual abuse, and did not pose a
OL,16,Frisk to the public.
OL,18,F"And yet, they were put through a
OL,19,Fdemeaning experience of police custody
OL,20,Fand, in some cases, strip search.
