OL,6,F"In all cases featured, there are
OL,7,Fexamples of extremely poor,
OL,8,Findefensible and inhumane treatment.
OL,10,F"A recurring pattern is what appears
OL,11,Fto be a lack of even-handedness in the
OL,12,Finvestigation of disputes, where the
OL,13,Fmore vulnerable person is reduced to a
OL,14,Fstate of even greater vulnerability
OL,15,Fand those posing a greater risk to
OL,16,Fpublic safety do not receive the same
OL,17,Fattention."
